snippet.title: Kayos for the Atari 8-bit family
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

---


Game description:

Kayos is an action game, set in the world of Kayos.

An asteroid bombardement has destroyed all ground life and the Kayotians took over.

It is your task to destroy the mothership of the Kayotians as many times as possible, before you lose all your lives. 


What I think:

While it is somewhat playable, it is not a good game...

There isn't much to the game and avoiding the smaller ships is annoying....REALLY annoying...
